01:02:59.760 --> 01:03:06.143
So this letter opens similarly to what we

01:03:06.344 --> 01:03:08.764
read earlier from Romans seven and that

01:03:08.804 --> 01:03:13.286
diatribe with universal condemnation.

01:03:14.248 --> 01:03:16.889
Generic statements like that seldom have

01:03:16.929 --> 01:03:17.489
any value.

01:03:17.849 --> 01:03:19.230
When you say, you know,

01:03:19.409 --> 01:03:23.271
all Greeks are overweight.

01:03:23.952 --> 01:03:26.333
No, some are, some aren't.

01:03:27.153 --> 01:03:28.815
Some people who are Greek are not Greek

01:03:28.974 --> 01:03:29.135
are.

01:03:29.815 --> 01:03:30.554
Some are not.

01:03:31.396 --> 01:03:36.898
Generalities like that never are even

01:03:37.018 --> 01:03:37.920
worth stating.

01:03:39.434 --> 01:03:40.635
So while it's appropriate to

01:03:41.034 --> 01:03:42.976
constructively criticize religious

01:03:43.317 --> 01:03:45.117
documents and institutions,

01:03:45.177 --> 01:03:47.278
it is not appropriate to rail against

01:03:47.318 --> 01:03:50.922
their victims en masse unless they become

01:03:50.961 --> 01:03:55.324
promoters and perpetrators of a lie that

01:03:55.425 --> 01:03:58.487
is damning to God's people or God's

01:03:58.507 --> 01:03:58.907
message.

01:03:59.367 --> 01:04:01.588
And yet Paul is lashing out at everyone

01:04:02.128 --> 01:04:04.329
while undermining the entire community

01:04:04.670 --> 01:04:07.032
because he suspects everyone is his foe.

01:04:07.172 --> 01:04:07.893
He's paranoid.

01:04:08.641 --> 01:04:11.824
including from heaven and down to earth.

01:04:12.324 --> 01:04:15.065
He feels compelled to cut them all down.

01:04:16.047 --> 01:04:17.047
So in this regard,

01:04:17.648 --> 01:04:20.409
his tone will evolve from condescending to

01:04:20.469 --> 01:04:24.813
vicious and will become stunningly

01:04:24.954 --> 01:04:27.996
uncivilized and uncultured.

01:04:28.036 --> 01:04:28.456
And while I

01:04:29.730 --> 01:04:33.954
never find it appropriate since Paul poses

01:04:33.994 --> 01:04:34.594
the question.

01:04:35.215 --> 01:04:37.737
His wholly antagonistic attitude towards

01:04:37.817 --> 01:04:41.300
men reveals the answer to the questions

01:04:41.340 --> 01:04:44.163
that he posed.

01:04:44.242 --> 01:04:47.065
In his mind, he was debating God.

01:04:48.766 --> 01:04:49.148
Moreover,

01:04:50.208 --> 01:04:52.409
the evidence will demonstrate Paul's rage

01:04:52.471 --> 01:04:54.813
was universally misplaced.

01:04:55.833 --> 01:04:58.576
Sha'uwl's adversaries were leading the

01:04:58.795 --> 01:05:01.737
Galatians to Yahowah, to the Towrah,

01:05:02.557 --> 01:05:04.900
while Sha'uwl's were taking them for a ride

01:05:04.940 --> 01:05:08.882
in the opposite direction.

01:05:08.922 --> 01:05:10.983
Now, apart from the errant title Christ,

01:05:11.704 --> 01:05:14.105
my concern with the most influential

01:05:14.806 --> 01:05:19.288
translations is that they were neither

01:05:19.347 --> 01:05:20.009
consistent

01:05:21.552 --> 01:05:23.893
with the actual text,

01:05:24.394 --> 01:05:28.257
and they added and removed words.

01:05:29.719 --> 01:05:32.360
They added a plethora of terms to

01:05:32.440 --> 01:05:34.822
artificially elevate the writing quality

01:05:35.543 --> 01:05:37.224
and removed ones that they did not

01:05:37.405 --> 01:05:39.327
understand or didn't fit their religion.

01:05:40.668 --> 01:05:41.469
Well, Paul wrote,

01:05:42.382 --> 01:05:44.724
For because currently or simultaneously,

01:05:44.923 --> 01:05:45.244
men,

01:05:45.485 --> 01:05:48.186
I presently persuade to win the favor of

01:05:48.266 --> 01:05:50.487
seducing, misleading, and coaxing,

01:05:50.606 --> 01:05:53.809
even conniving and appeasing, placating,

01:05:53.849 --> 01:05:57.130
and alternatively, the theos, God.

01:05:58.110 --> 01:05:59.612
Or alternatively,

01:05:59.672 --> 01:06:01.432
by comparison and contrast,

01:06:02.092 --> 01:06:05.375
I desire to please and accommodate humans.

01:06:06.380 --> 01:06:07.239
Yet nevertheless,

01:06:07.420 --> 01:06:11.641
even regardless if men I was obliging and

01:06:11.740 --> 01:06:14.842
accommodating, exciting them emotionally,

01:06:15.101 --> 01:06:23.043
a slave of Christo certainly not was me.

01:06:23.402 --> 01:06:25.043
With that being what he wrote,

01:06:25.643 --> 01:06:27.864
the King James Version published,

01:06:29.083 --> 01:06:33.864
for do I now persuade men or God?

01:06:34.873 --> 01:06:37.695
Or do I seek to please men?

01:06:38.695 --> 01:06:41.458
For if I yet pleased men,

01:06:42.137 --> 01:06:47.001
I should not be the servant of Christ.

01:06:47.041 --> 01:06:49.302
While Christians no Dowd see this as a

01:06:49.362 --> 01:06:50.443
rhetorical question,

01:06:50.824 --> 01:06:53.126
the deeper we dig into Paul's mantra and

01:06:53.186 --> 01:06:53.726
mindset,

01:06:54.326 --> 01:06:56.427
the more likely it becomes that Paul

01:06:56.487 --> 01:06:59.110
thought himself qualified to persuade God

01:06:59.630 --> 01:07:01.630
to change his plan of salvation.

01:07:02.891 --> 01:07:03.753
The living

01:07:04.661 --> 01:07:07.003
of the Latin Vulgate, right?

01:07:07.023 --> 01:07:08.603
And this would be the Latin Vulgate

01:07:08.702 --> 01:07:09.583
rendered in English.

01:07:10.623 --> 01:07:13.585
For am I now persuading men or God?

01:07:14.065 --> 01:07:16.505
Or am I seeking to please men?

01:07:16.626 --> 01:07:19.447
If I still were pleasing men,

01:07:19.907 --> 01:07:22.487
then I would not be a servant of

01:07:22.547 --> 01:07:24.768
Christie.

01:07:24.829 --> 01:07:24.949
Now,

01:07:25.048 --> 01:07:28.530
unlike the King James and the Vulgate,

01:07:29.271 --> 01:07:31.132
the New Living Translations reads

01:07:31.192 --> 01:07:31.711
beautifully.

01:07:32.478 --> 01:07:35.099
It's a shame Paul didn't write this

01:07:35.199 --> 01:07:36.280
eloquently.

01:07:36.840 --> 01:07:37.561
Obviously,

01:07:38.242 --> 01:07:40.304
I'm not trying to win the approval of

01:07:40.344 --> 01:07:42.065
people, but of God.

01:07:43.186 --> 01:07:45.067
If pleasing men were my goal,

01:07:45.608 --> 01:07:47.469
I would not be Christ's servant.

01:07:47.668 --> 01:07:51.172
Well,

01:07:51.192 --> 01:07:54.293
there is an extremely remote possibility

01:07:54.713 --> 01:07:56.815
that this may have been what he meant

01:07:56.856 --> 01:07:57.356
to say.

01:07:57.876 --> 01:07:59.637
It is absolutely not what he wrote.

01:08:02.724 --> 01:08:05.286
And should they have magically captured

01:08:05.346 --> 01:08:06.485
Paul's intent,

01:08:07.427 --> 01:08:10.168
we are incapable of winning the approval

01:08:10.188 --> 01:08:10.568
of God.

01:08:13.509 --> 01:08:16.170
That is the reason God conceived a plan

01:08:16.670 --> 01:08:19.712
whereby he did all that was required to

01:08:19.731 --> 01:08:21.891
make us acceptable.

01:08:21.992 --> 01:08:23.533
Next.

01:08:23.613 --> 01:08:26.793
We find Sha'uwl professing that the message

01:08:26.833 --> 01:08:29.295
he was revealing was his own.

01:08:30.376 --> 01:08:31.256
And indeed it was.

01:08:32.560 --> 01:08:35.081
And Paulos wanted everyone the world over

01:08:35.140 --> 01:08:37.582
to recognize that the mantra which would

01:08:37.622 --> 01:08:40.082
become known as the gospel.

01:08:41.564 --> 01:08:43.104
The fact that there's four gospels

01:08:43.805 --> 01:08:47.146
preceding Paul's letters doesn't mean

01:08:47.186 --> 01:08:48.987
that's how they were conceived.

01:08:49.106 --> 01:08:51.529
It's Paul that conceived the concept of a

01:08:51.588 --> 01:08:53.869
gospel and the first of them would not

01:08:53.930 --> 01:08:56.371
be written until two and a half,

01:08:56.451 --> 01:08:59.152
three decades after this letter that

01:08:59.192 --> 01:09:00.972
introduced the concept of gospel.

01:09:01.948 --> 01:09:03.631
and they were written by two of Paul's

01:09:03.671 --> 01:09:07.694
cronies.

01:09:07.774 --> 01:09:13.759
It was hypo-ego is the basis of it,

01:09:14.319 --> 01:09:17.542
by, under and through me, hyper-ego,

01:09:18.203 --> 01:09:19.724
by reason and force of me,

01:09:20.625 --> 01:09:24.108
because of and controlled by me and my

01:09:24.268 --> 01:09:24.608
ego.

01:09:26.970 --> 01:09:27.230
But,

01:09:27.886 --> 01:09:32.911
Therefore, however, I profess, not God,

01:09:33.771 --> 01:09:36.734
not Yahowah, not even Jesus,

01:09:38.155 --> 01:09:41.819
but therefore I profess and I reveal,

01:09:43.539 --> 01:09:44.980
I perceive and I tell,

01:09:45.101 --> 01:09:47.623
I provide the knowledge I have gained to

01:09:47.663 --> 01:09:48.243
make known,

01:09:48.604 --> 01:09:51.806
I recognize and declare to you, brothers,

01:09:52.106 --> 01:09:53.167
he doesn't have any brothers.

01:09:54.248 --> 01:09:54.909
They all hated him, remember?

01:09:54.930 --> 01:09:55.170
Remember?

01:09:57.654 --> 01:09:59.675
of the beneficial messenger and the

01:09:59.715 --> 01:10:00.555
healing message.

01:10:01.256 --> 01:10:01.496
Huh?

01:10:02.136 --> 01:10:04.957
Brothers of the beneficial messenger or of

01:10:04.997 --> 01:10:05.898
the healing message?

01:10:05.938 --> 01:10:06.859
Is he out of his mind?

01:10:07.859 --> 01:10:08.800
Which they all rejected.

01:10:08.819 --> 01:10:11.100
And he just affirmed they rejected it.

01:10:11.140 --> 01:10:12.881
So there are no brothers of that message,

01:10:13.523 --> 01:10:16.043
which having been communicated

01:10:16.304 --> 01:10:20.645
advantageously by myself, ego,

01:10:21.966 --> 01:10:25.149
because it was not in accord with man.

01:10:28.970 --> 01:10:29.029
Huh?

01:10:29.050 --> 01:10:30.390
Galatians one, eleven.

01:10:31.430 --> 01:10:32.011
This, of course,

01:10:32.051 --> 01:10:34.891
means that Paul was solely responsible for

01:10:34.932 --> 01:10:35.832
his gospel.

01:10:36.412 --> 01:10:38.394
He conceived it all by himself.

01:10:39.694 --> 01:10:42.234
And he alone was authorized to declare it

01:10:42.814 --> 01:10:43.576
his gospel.

01:10:43.775 --> 01:10:45.275
After all, as such,

01:10:45.336 --> 01:10:47.317
Paul was solely responsible for the

01:10:47.337 --> 01:10:50.938
mythology which became Christianity.

01:10:52.639 --> 01:10:55.560
There is no one else to credit or

01:10:55.600 --> 01:10:56.060
to blame.

01:10:57.904 --> 01:11:00.725
If his proposal and individual revelations

01:11:00.784 --> 01:11:02.445
are not true, and they aren't,

01:11:03.345 --> 01:11:06.346
the religion he conceived is wholly

01:11:06.487 --> 01:11:07.167
unreliable.

01:11:08.327 --> 01:11:10.627
Christian clerics universally recognize

01:11:10.747 --> 01:11:13.729
and readily admit that Paul opposed the

01:11:13.908 --> 01:11:15.090
alleged disciples.

01:11:16.170 --> 01:11:17.789
The statement merely explains why.

01:11:18.770 --> 01:11:20.131
His message was his own,

01:11:20.770 --> 01:11:22.252
and he did not play well with others.

01:11:25.292 --> 01:11:28.274
Set into the context of debating God,

01:11:29.073 --> 01:11:33.595
this is an incriminating confession.

01:11:33.636 --> 01:11:35.356
But even if you were unaware of Paul's

01:11:35.417 --> 01:11:37.677
underhanded slap at his adversaries,

01:11:37.717 --> 01:11:38.957
both human and divine,

01:11:39.998 --> 01:11:46.480
it was either egregiously presumptuous or

01:11:47.341 --> 01:11:51.103
an outrageous confession, one of the two.

01:11:53.462 --> 01:11:55.101
We're dealing with presumptiveness or

01:11:55.162 --> 01:11:55.802
confessions.

01:11:56.403 --> 01:12:00.345
To write, gnoso, I reveal, I provide.

01:12:00.845 --> 01:12:02.506
The euangelion,

01:12:02.525 --> 01:12:04.226
the beneficial messenger and the healing

01:12:04.247 --> 01:12:04.707
messenger.

01:12:04.806 --> 01:12:06.667
And I, euangelio,

01:12:06.728 --> 01:12:09.128
communicate it advantageously.

01:12:09.630 --> 01:12:12.850
Hypo, ego, by myself.

01:12:12.871 --> 01:12:17.333
It's a confession.

01:12:19.614 --> 01:12:21.576
If Paul were somehow speaking for God,

01:12:22.898 --> 01:12:25.759
Shouldn't he be touting Yahowah's words and

01:12:25.779 --> 01:12:26.259
not his own?

01:12:26.880 --> 01:12:27.520
It's that another way.

01:12:28.279 --> 01:12:31.001
Someone who is speaking for Yahowah knows

01:12:31.020 --> 01:12:33.921
that it's his message, Yahowah's message,

01:12:33.942 --> 01:12:36.722
that matters, not the one who delivers it.

01:12:38.684 --> 01:12:41.324
Had this been anything more than Paul

01:12:41.385 --> 01:12:45.006
claiming the world as his own,

01:12:45.065 --> 01:12:50.547
he would have done what he was doing.

01:12:51.529 --> 01:12:51.969
And he would...

01:12:52.970 --> 01:12:54.530
do as what we are doing,

01:12:54.591 --> 01:12:59.414
which is to dissect every errant message,

01:12:59.435 --> 01:13:02.056
showing through evidence and reason where

01:13:02.936 --> 01:13:03.358
it's wrong.

01:13:03.757 --> 01:13:08.461
He claimed that the gospel was his own.

01:13:08.501 --> 01:13:10.403
So they don't have a gospel of Matthew,

01:13:10.443 --> 01:13:11.222
Mark, Luke, and John.

01:13:11.262 --> 01:13:12.864
No, the gospel is Paul's.

01:13:13.345 --> 01:13:14.365
He invented the concept.

01:13:14.945 --> 01:13:17.167
He doesn't take any rivals,

01:13:17.728 --> 01:13:19.609
and he argued with God to create his

01:13:19.930 --> 01:13:20.250
version.

01:13:22.634 --> 01:13:25.033
And he then claimed that his message alone

01:13:25.073 --> 01:13:27.375
would stand and anyone who had a different

01:13:27.414 --> 01:13:32.256
gospel than his was cursed.

01:13:32.296 --> 01:13:34.015
Paul should have delineated pertinent

01:13:34.055 --> 01:13:35.876
examples of his euangelion,

01:13:37.237 --> 01:13:39.096
which may be different from his own,

01:13:39.697 --> 01:13:40.296
but he didn't.

01:13:41.737 --> 01:13:45.177
But the only message Paul has condemned is

01:13:45.238 --> 01:13:45.717
God's.

01:13:46.057 --> 01:13:47.859
He was ruthless towards the Towrah,

01:13:48.019 --> 01:13:50.059
discrediting and discarding God's Towrah.

01:13:51.840 --> 01:13:54.780
His enemy is God.

01:13:54.841 --> 01:13:57.862
His victims are known as Christians.

01:13:59.882 --> 01:14:01.703
The McReynolds Interlinear reveals that

01:14:01.743 --> 01:14:03.385
the Nestle-Allen text reads,

01:14:03.864 --> 01:14:07.225
I make known for to you, brothers,

01:14:07.765 --> 01:14:08.707
the good message,

01:14:09.067 --> 01:14:13.788
having been told good message by me that

01:14:13.868 --> 01:14:17.109
not it is by man.

01:14:17.149 --> 01:14:19.211
So that's saying I'm not a man.

01:14:20.967 --> 01:14:22.010
I was the one who told you the

01:14:22.050 --> 01:14:26.614
message, but it's not by man.

01:14:28.037 --> 01:14:28.998
I told you the message,

01:14:29.378 --> 01:14:31.100
but it's not by man.

01:14:31.521 --> 01:14:32.582
What does that make Paul?

01:14:33.363 --> 01:14:34.164
A wannabe God.

01:14:35.926 --> 01:14:37.349
In order to make those words appear

01:14:37.429 --> 01:14:37.810
credible,

01:14:38.552 --> 01:14:41.194
euangelion and euangelizo had to be

01:14:41.255 --> 01:14:42.095
rendered differently,

01:14:42.154 --> 01:14:44.155
even though their etymological basis is

01:14:44.235 --> 01:14:44.697
identical.

01:14:45.556 --> 01:14:47.057
But yet in the King James, they said,

01:14:47.097 --> 01:14:51.720
but I clarify, I certify you, brethren,

01:14:52.261 --> 01:14:54.943
that the gospel which was preached of me,

01:14:55.382 --> 01:14:59.945
gospel of me, is not after man.

01:14:59.966 --> 01:15:01.265
Then why doesn't God have a gospel?

01:15:03.728 --> 01:15:03.787
Hmm?

01:15:05.457 --> 01:15:06.418
Well, that's incriminating.

01:15:06.640 --> 01:15:08.802
The King James Version accurately asserted

01:15:08.863 --> 01:15:12.028
that Paul certified that the gospel which

01:15:12.068 --> 01:15:14.631
was preached was of me.

01:15:16.074 --> 01:15:16.996
in a rational world,

01:15:17.655 --> 01:15:20.578
this would have been sufficient to bury

01:15:20.599 --> 01:15:21.600
him.

01:15:21.619 --> 01:15:24.162
Jerome's blend of old Latin text was both

01:15:24.362 --> 01:15:26.863
less accurate and less convincing.

01:15:27.463 --> 01:15:28.625
The Latin Vulgate reads,

01:15:29.145 --> 01:15:31.608
For I would have you understand, brothers,

01:15:32.007 --> 01:15:33.970
that the euangelium,

01:15:34.149 --> 01:15:40.574
which has been euangelisatum by me,

01:15:41.095 --> 01:15:42.796
was not according to man.

01:15:44.500 --> 01:15:47.220
then where is God's proof text on it?

01:15:48.921 --> 01:15:51.601
I've translated most of the Towrah prophets

01:15:51.622 --> 01:15:52.202
and Psalms.

01:15:53.502 --> 01:15:55.662
I've analyzed God's words, his message.

01:15:56.663 --> 01:16:00.425
I don't find a gospel anywhere in it,

01:16:01.265 --> 01:16:03.865
nor do I find the cute little gratia

01:16:03.945 --> 01:16:07.627
or the charis, the charities.

01:16:07.867 --> 01:16:09.407
I find a Paul mentioned,

01:16:09.787 --> 01:16:11.627
and God says that he's the plague of

01:16:11.667 --> 01:16:11.988
death.

01:16:14.966 --> 01:16:16.506
That's not helpful to Christians, is it?

01:16:21.349 --> 01:16:25.211
But never and ever inform the New Living

01:16:25.251 --> 01:16:29.453
Translation ignored six of the twelve

01:16:29.493 --> 01:16:30.073
Greek words.

01:16:32.194 --> 01:16:35.296
And then they added ten English words of

01:16:35.317 --> 01:16:36.056
their own choosing.

01:16:38.497 --> 01:16:40.738
If you can't convey the meaning of the

01:16:40.757 --> 01:16:42.099
words in the text,

01:16:42.539 --> 01:16:44.640
then don't pretend that it is a

01:16:44.701 --> 01:16:45.981
translation, okay?

01:16:46.221 --> 01:16:50.805
Just said we're writing a novel.

01:16:50.886 --> 01:16:52.447
Still inadequate to support their

01:16:52.506 --> 01:16:53.108
theology,

01:16:53.648 --> 01:16:55.469
they grossly misinterpreted and

01:16:55.509 --> 01:16:58.851
misrepresented and inconsistently

01:16:58.931 --> 01:17:03.756
translated euangelion.

01:17:03.796 --> 01:17:05.096
Dear brothers and sisters,

01:17:06.100 --> 01:17:08.202
I want you to understand the gospel

01:17:08.242 --> 01:17:11.101
message I preach is not based upon mere

01:17:11.162 --> 01:17:16.002
human reasoning.

01:17:16.023 --> 01:17:18.203
The use of mere implies that human

01:17:18.243 --> 01:17:20.744
reasoning was a contributing factor.

01:17:21.545 --> 01:17:23.265
And that suggests that Yahowah's message

01:17:23.305 --> 01:17:26.945
was incomplete or inadequate and that he

01:17:27.006 --> 01:17:29.546
required the contribution of Sha'uwl's

01:17:29.587 --> 01:17:30.747
considerable intellect.

01:17:31.837 --> 01:17:33.578
When you combine Paul's arrogant and

01:17:33.639 --> 01:17:35.400
incriminating statements with the

01:17:35.440 --> 01:17:37.243
Christian interpretation of them,

01:17:37.662 --> 01:17:42.307
you have the crime and the confession laid

01:17:42.347 --> 01:17:43.109
right at your feet.

